uat, namun memerlukan dukungan infrastruktur yang memadai.", "Call_to_Ac": "\"Harmonisasikan pertumbuhan ekonomi kerakyatan dengan penataan lingkungan!\"\nTerletak di kawasan padat penduduk yang strategis, wilayah ini memiliki potensi besar dalam perdagangan dan jasa skala lokal. Meski demikian, permasalahan sanitasi, pengelolaan limbah, dan tingginya risiko kebakaran permukiman menuntut penanganan spasial yang komprehensif."}, "geometry": {"type": "Polygon", "coordinates": [[[113.91118062438011, -2.194448422283756], [113.91095250892647, -2.1949337312404964], [113.91054251139633, -2.195800625493348], [113.9102394697436, -2.1964418894116875], [113.9098591821795, -2.197267219419814], [113.90949672059503, -2.1980272351390795], [113.90896788320106, -2.1992978855553247], [113.9069317602009, -2.1984203550970847], [113.90724074384684, -2.1971853296821564], [113.90732393175142, -2.1970131385576224], [113.90766856735661, -2.196419375906828], [113.90806668090033, -2.195807800129785], [113.90855392434219, -2.1951546606741204], [113.90900551582445, -2.194673712346969], [113.90965913507546, -2.1939315078347477], [113.90983030054974, -2.1937155697838193], [113.90993146975507, -2.193760773045767], [113.91041331060865, -2.194034411061466], [113.91069289727682, -2.1941890760267597], [113.91091299742004, -2.1942961517721074], [113.91118062438011, -2.194448422283756]]]}}, {"type": "Feature", "properties": {"fid": 4, "Id": 12, "Kawasan": "Kawasan XII", "Luas_Ha": "21,2034801336792", "Lokasi": "", "Kelurahan": "PALANGKA", "Kecamatan": "JEKAN RAYA", "Kondisi_Ba": "23%", "Kondisi_Ja": "20%", "Kondisi_ai": "11%", "Kondisi_Dr": "11%", "Kondisi__1": "54%", "Kondisi_Pe": "52%", "Kondisi_Pr": "50%", "Potensi_1": "1. Area Padat Interaksi: Fungsi campuran antara permukiman rapat dan ruang usaha menjadikannya wilayah yang dinamis namun rentan.\n2. Pengembangan Ekonomi Mikro: Sangat potensial untuk diberdayakan menjadi klaster usaha masyarakat yang tangguh dengan perbaikan kualitas tata ruang.", "Call_to_Ac": "\"Integrasikan potensi niaga mandiri dengan peningkatan ketahanan kawasan!\"\nDengan lokasinya yang vital, area ini tumbuh sebagai pusat interaksi ekonomi. Tantangan utamanya adalah bagaimana mengelola kepadatan ini agar tidak memicu masalah lingkungan turunan, seperti sanitasi buruk dan rawan api."}, "geometry": {"type": "Polygon", "coordinates": [[[113.91468540855624, -2.1930859009271444], [113.91464298507253, -2.1945611561653777], [113.91455766170293, -2.1967779350535466], [113.91380468867328, -2.196941195912075], [113.91349095143278, -2.19700532226733], [113.9129704328293, -2.1971478252691554], [113.91277791224991, -2.197204826466077], [113.9120577426753, -2.197354454597644], [113.9109810535092, -2.197639460520975], [113.91026088393448, -2.1978104640489278], [113.90991149473496, -2.1978959658055146], [113.90966193102099, -2.1980028429944127], [113.90940908217635, -2.198237806165025], [113.9098591821795, -2.197267219419814], [113.9102394697436, -2.1964418894116875], [113.91054251139633, -2.195800625493348], [113.91095250892647, -2.1949337312404964], [113.91132091250438, -2.194149963401003], [113.91183192391873, -2.19322962942897], [113.911998299728, -2.192932747381633], [113.91210939699056, -2.1927436091646655], [113.91272773301353, -2.1930865924273917], [113.91325121443492, -2.1922002432028194], [113.91468540855624, -2.1930859009271444]]]}}, {"type": "Feature", "properties": {"fid": 5, "Id": 3, "Kawasan": "Kawasan III", "Luas_Ha": "17,2353848869665", "Lokasi": "RT001-RW008,RT001-RW009,RT002-RW007,RT003-RW008,RT004-RW007,RT004-RW009", "Kelurahan": "PAHANDUT", "Kecamatan": "PAHANDUT", "Kondisi_Ba": "48%", "Kondisi_Ja": "25%", "Kondisi_ai": "39%", "Kondisi_Dr": "0%", "Kondisi__1": "30%", "Kondisi_Pe": "50%", "Kondisi_Pr": "100%", "Potensi_1": "1. Ekonomi Kreatif dan UMKM Berbasis Budaya: Pengembangan kerajinan tangan lokal, kuliner khas Dayak, untuk mendukung pariwisata.\n\n2. Sektor Perdagangan dan Jasa: Peningkatan sarana dan prasarana perdagangan, mengingat wilayah Jekan Raya merupakan kawasa", "Call_to_Ac": "\"Bawa napas baru untuk permukiman di jantung kota!\"\nKawasan ini memiliki peluang besar untuk pengembangan Urban Farming dan perniagaan. Namun, para warga masih menghadapi tantangan serius pada pemenuhan air bersih, sistem drainase, dan penataan letak bangunan yang padat."}, "geometry": {"type": "Polygon", "coordinates": [[[113.93933437059505, -2.2105003541984156], [113.93949480441131, -2.2100431611192746], [113.93966118022055, -2.2095147169952085], [113.93991074393465, -2.208653768300524], [113.93998204785296, -2.208220324975744], [113.93999987383248, -2.207893758003646], [113.94047523328771, -2.2078700076755937], [113.9409624767293, -2.20782844460061], [113.94134870628669, -2.2077809439421214], [113.94172899385084, -2.2077512560297112], [113.94299463840039, -2.20772156811676], [113.94333927400542, -2.207703755368749], [113.94349376582839, -2.2077393808645995], [113.94392158933807, -2.20782844460061], [113.94379680748119, -2.208327201423735], [113.9435294177875, -2.2094019030567087], [113.94349376582839, -2.209585967899307], [113.94371956156958, -2.2096631563748823], [113.94354724376709, -2.2103816027627627], [113.94387405339255, -2.210535979627182], [113.94340463593048, -2.211569116691128], [113.9423113091835, -2.211729430998683], [113.94128334436148, -2.2112900510033953], [113.94002364180513, -2.21072004432919], [113.93933437059505, -2.2105003541984156]]]}}, {"type": "Feature", "properties": {"fid": 6, "Id": 2, "Kawasan": "Kawasan II", "Luas_Ha": "18,1137391638852", "Lokasi": "RT001-RW006,RT003-RW006,RT004-RW006,RT004-RW006", "Kelurahan": "PAHANDUT", "Kecamatan": "PAHANDUT", "Kondisi_Ba": "48%", "Kondisi_Ja": "9%", "Kondisi_ai": "21%", "Kondisi_Dr": "5%", "Kondisi__1": "35%", "Kondisi_Pe": "67%", "Kondisi_Pr": "100%", "Potensi_1": "1. Ekonomi Kreatif dan UMKM Berbasis Budaya: Pengembangan kerajinan tangan lokal, kuliner khas Dayak, untuk mendukung pariwisata.\n\n2. Sektor Perdagangan dan Jasa: Penin